    "content": "This example demonstrates how to use the SPI driver in synchronous mode to achieve self-loop back between multiple clients in RTOS environment. ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/core_apps_sam_e70_s70_v70_v71/apps/driver/spi/sync/spi_self_loopback_multi_client/readme.html#spi-driver-synchronous---self-loopback-multi-client",
