    "title": "Description",
    "content": "File System Operations on NVM: . | The application contains a MPFS disk image in the internal Flash memory. The disk image contains two files named: . | FILE.txt, Size = 11 Bytes. The content of the file is: “Hello World” | TEST.txt, Size = 10 Bytes. The content of the file is: “1234567890” | . | The application performs following file system related operations: . | SYS_FS_FileRead | SYS_FS_FileStat | SYS_FS_FileSize | SYS_FS_FileSeek | SYS_FS_FileEOF | . | The contents of both the files are read and compared with the expected strings as mentioned above. If the string compare is successful, An LED indication is provided. | . ",
